e heart of man."]],[11,["We, Joseph Smith, Jun., and Sidney Rigdon, being ",["in",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rev. 1:10","nt/rev/1.10"],"; ",["4:2","nt/rev/4.2"],"."]]]," the Spirit on the sixteenth day of February, in the year of our Lord one thousand eight hundred and thirty-two—"]],[12,["By the power of the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Transfiguration","tg/transfiguration"],"."]]]," our ",["eyes",["study-note-ref","b",[["Eph. 1:18","nt/eph/1.18"],"; ",["D&C 11:13","dc-testament/dc/11.13"],"; ",["110:1","dc-testament/dc/110.1"],"; ",["137:1","dc-testament/dc/137.1"],"; ",["138:11 (11, 29)","dc-testament/dc/138.11"],". ",["TG God, Privilege of Seeing","tg/god-privilege-of-seeing"],"."]]]," were opened and our understandings were enlightened, so as to see and understand the things of God—"]],[13,["Even those things which were from the beginning before the world was, which were ordained of the Father, through his Only Begotten Son, who was in the bosom of the Father, even from the ",["beginning",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Foreordained","tg/jesus-christ-foreordained"],"."]]],";"]],[14,["Of whom we bear record; and ",["",138],"the record which we bear is the fulness of the gospel of Jesus Christ, who is the Son, whom we saw and with whom we ",["conversed",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 109:57","dc-testament/dc/109.57"],"."]]]," in the heavenly ",["vision",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Vision","tg/vision"],"."]]],"."]],[15,["For while we were doing the work of ",["translation",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 73:3 (3–4)","dc-testament/dc/73.3"],"; ",["93:53","dc-testament/dc/93.53"],"."]]],", which the Lord had appointed unto us, we came to the ",["twenty-ninth verse of the fifth chapter of John",["scripture-ref"]],", which was given unto us as follows—"]],[16,["Speaking of the resurrection of the dead, concerning those who shall ",["hear",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 5:28","nt/john/5.28"],"."]]]," the voice of the ",["Son of Man",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Son of Man","tg/jesus-christ-son-of-man"],"."]]],":"]],[17,["And shall come forth; ",["they",["study-note-ref","a",["Joseph Smith Translation has the same wording as used here, which differs from the King James Version of ",["John 5:29","nt/john/5.29"],"."]]]," who have done ",["good",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Good Works","tg/good-works"],"."]]],", in the ",["resurrection",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Resurrection","tg/resurrection"],"."]]]," of the ",["just",["study-note-ref","d",[["Dan. 12:2 (1–3)","ot/dan/12.2"],"; ",["Acts 24:15","nt/acts/24.15"],"; ",["D&C 76:65 (50, 64–65)","dc-testament/dc/76.65"],"."]]],"; and they who have done evil, in the resurrection of the unjust."]],[18,["Now this caused us to marvel, for it was given unto us of the Spirit."]],[19,["And while we ",["meditated",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Ne. 11:1","bofm/1-ne/11.1"],"; ",["D&C 138:11 (1, 11)","dc-testament/dc/138.11"],"; ",["JS—H 1:44","pgp/js-h/1.44"],". ",["TG Meditation","tg/meditation"],"."]]]," upon these things, the Lord touched the eyes of our understandings and they were opened, and the ",["glory",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Glory of","tg/god-glory-of"],"."]]]," of the Lord shone round about."]],[20,["And we beheld the ",["glory",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Glory of","tg/jesus-christ-glory-of"],"."]]]," of the Son, on the ",["right hand",["study-note-ref","b",[["Acts 7:56","nt/acts/7.56"],"; ",["D&C 49:6","dc-testament/dc/49.6"],"; ",["104:7","dc-testament/dc/104.7"],"."]]]," of the ",["Father",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG God the Father, Elohim","tg/god-the-father-elohim"],"."]]],", and received of his fulness;"]],[21,["And saw the holy ",["angels",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 25:31","nt/matt/25.31"],"; ",["2 Thes. 1:7","nt/2-thes/1.7"],"; ",["Heb. 12:22","nt/heb/12.22"],"; ",["D&C 130:7","dc-testament/dc/130.7"],"; ",["136:37","dc-testament/dc/136.37"],"."]]],", and them who are ",["sanctified",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Sanctification",